  "title": "Sales Engineer (Tuas, Mechanical/Industrial)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Support the preparation of sales proposals, costings, and technical documentation for mechanical and industrial solutions.</li><li>Provide basic technical clarifications to clients and assist in coordinating follow-ups on enquiries.</li><li>Help the team identify potential leads, collect market insights, and track ongoing opportunities.</li><li>Work with internal engineers to verify specifications, solution details, and project requirements.</li><li>Assist with customer servicing tasks, including updates, coordination, and post-delivery technical matters.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical Engineering or related fields.</li><li>Around 3 years of experience in <strong>technical support, engineering assistance, or sales engineering roles.</strong></li><li>Working knowledge of <strong>mechanical systems, machinery, or industrial equipment.</strong></li><li>Able to communicate technical concepts clearly to both customers and internal teams.</li><li>Strong organisational skills, proactive work attitude, and willingness to take on client-facing tasks.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
